  "text": "Okay, George, I shall know. I and Rob. There were two contacts which gave the entity with vibratory sound complex George this information. One was of the configuration. The second was of the Orion Group, the Confederation was caused to find the distortion towards non-contact due to the alteration of the vibrational mind complex patterns of the one called Georgia. Thus the Orion group used this instrument. However, this instrument, though confused, was a mind, a body, a spirit, complex, devoted at the heart to service, to others. So the shall we say worst that could be done was to disacredit this source.",
